suncertify.gui.client
Class Mediator

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.commons.LoggingObject
      suncertify.gui.client.Mediator

public final class Mediator
extends LoggingObject

Executes BusinessCommands and broadcast the event to the subscribed listeners.
Execution of the commands can be made synchronously or asynchronously. Listeners notification thread is:

  • in case of synchronous execution listeners are notified in the same thread
  • in case of asynchronous execution listeners are notified in the AWT event dispatching thread.

executeCommandSync

public <R> R executeCommandSync(BusinessCommand<R> cmd)
                     throws Exception
Executes the command in the current thread. Result object and possible exceptions thrown are returned to the caller in the common way, but also are notified to all the registered listerners.

Type Parameters:
R - the class of the command target method result type.
Parameters:
